---
title: Tom's Mexican Tortilla Stack with Sour Cream & Spring Onion
description: Tom is in our HR team but we're starting to think he ought to be in the kitchen! We invited him into a brainstorming session and he suggested this Mexican take on lasagne. It sounded totally crazy, but it totally works. You get all the luscious layers and cheesy topping of lasagne, but in half the time and with delicious Mexican flavours. Winning!
